fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.design

Interface IPageContext

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDashboardContext, IFormContext, IListContext

    public interface IPageContext
    Provides access to page processing context for page implementations.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be safe for concurrent read/write access.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies

      • beforeDataMerge

        void beforeDataMerge(ITemplateData templateData)
        Allows modification of the data to be merged into the template.
        Parameters:
        templateData - the current container for data to be merged into the page template. The contents can be changed before being merged into the template file by the template engine.
        Since:
        1.0

      • filterTemplateMerge

        FilterWriter filterTemplateMerge(Writer out)
        Optionally filters the output of the template merge. This is a low-level filter function, and it will not be called for binary-only template files.

        When this is not required, this method should return null.

        Parameters:
        out - the output writer being used by the template engine.
        Returns:
        a filter writer that wraps the specified writer, or null to skip filtering.
        Since:
        1.0
